htmltools 0.2.5
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Explicit library(htmltools) is no longer required for tags to be rendered in 
  knitr/rmarkdown documents.

* Added "viewer" parameter to html_print.

* Added "includeSrcDir" parameter to htmlDependency. Lets the caller specify
  that the HTML dependency doesn't require its entire directory, just the
  individual script and/or stylesheet files that are named.



htmltools 0.2.4
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Initial release
